01 Feb 2021 16:35:50 +0800</pubDate></item><item><title>【饲料养殖周报】囤粮成本支撑玉米期价，供需改善利空肉蛋</title><link>https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/pcY0azd4bB2WnxT8i8WUUA</link><description></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ibQHo8uia0icSPuveGIFptuSDaS2Dib8ibennCGbO5q7N3Esu5m12RY9PEHlzOlfPsibZwfkZmb4ZcqSLWltyxmxITlQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br>玉米：囤粮成本支撑，预计下跌空间有限
